\c 6
\s Kuputswa kweguta reJeriko
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jeriko raiva rapfigwa kwazvo nekuda kwevana vaIsraeri; hakuna waibuda uye hakuna waipinda.
\v 2 Jehovha ndokuti kuna Joshua: Tarira, ndapa muruoko rwako Jeriko namambo waro \add ne\add*vakasimba\x + Det. 7.24. 2.24.\x* veumhare\x + 1.14.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino muchakomba guta, varume vose vehondo, poteredzai guta kamwe. Muchaita saizvozvo mazuva matanhatu.
\v 4 Zvino vapristi vanomwe vachatakura mberi kweareka hwamanda\x + Vato. 7.16,22.\x* nomwe\x + 6.6,8,13; 6.5.\x* dzenyanga dzemakondohwe; uye nezuva rechinomwe muchapoteredza guta kanomwe; uye vapristi vachiridza hwamanda\x + Num.. 10.8.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino zvichaitika, pavakaridza runyanga rwegondohwe nguva refu\x + Eki. 19.13. Vato. 20.37.\x*, pamunonzwa kurira kwehwamanda, vanhu vose vachadanidzira nekudanidzira kukuru; zvino rusvingo rweguta rwuchakoromoka, nevanhu vachakwira, umwe neumwe pakaruramana naye.
\p
\v 6 Zvino Joshua mwanakomana waNuni wakadana vapristi ndokuti kwavari: Simudzai areka yesungano, uye vapristi vanomwe vatakure hwamanda dzenyanga dzemakondohwe nomwe pamberi peareka yaJehovha.
\v 7 Zvino wakati kuvanhu: Pfuurai, poteredzai guta; neakashonga zvombo ngaapfuure pamberi peareka yaJehovha.
\p
\v 8 Zvino zvakaitika apo Joshua ataura kuvanhu, kuti vapristi vanomwe vakatakura hwamanda dzenyanga dzemakondohwe nomwe vakapfuura pamberi paJehovha ndokuridza hwamanda; areka yesungano yaJehovha ndokuvatevera.
\v 9 Zvino vakashonga zvombo vakafamba mberi kwevapristi vairidza hwamanda, neveshure vakatevera areka, ndokufamba vachiridza hwamanda.
\v 10 Zvino Joshua wakaraira vanhu achiti: Musadanidzira, kana kunzwisa manzwi enyu, uye kusabuda shoko mumuromo menyu, kusvika pazuva rekuti kwangu kwauri: Danidzirai; ipapo muchadanidzira.
\v 11 Naizvozvo achapoteredzesa areka yaJehovha guta, ichipoteredza kamwe; zvino vakauya kumusasa, ndokurara mumusasa.
\p
\v 12 Zvino Joshua wakamuka mangwanani-ngwanani, uye vapristi vakasimudza areka yaJehovha\x + Num.. 4.15.\x*.
\v 13 Nevapristi vanomwe vaiva vakatakura hwamanda dzenyanga dzemakondohwe nomwe mberi kweareka yaJehovha vakaenderera mberi vachifamba vachiridza hwamanda; nevakashonga zvombo vakafamba mberi kwavo; nevarindi veshure vakatevera areka yaJehovha, vakafamba vachingoridza hwamanda.
\v 14 Nezuva rechipiri vakapoteredza guta kamwe ndokudzokera kumusasa; vakaita saizvozvo mazuva matanhatu.
\p
\v 15 Zvino zvakaitika nezuva rechinomwe kuti vakamuka mangwanani mambakwedza ndokupoteredza guta nenzira iyoyo kanomwe; nezuva iro koga vakapoteredza guta kanomwe.
\v 16 Zvino zvakaitika panguva yechinomwe vapristi pavakaridza hwamanda, Joshua ndokuti kuvanhu: Danidzirai, nokuti Jehovha wakupai guta.
\v 17 Asi guta iro nechose chiri mariri zvichayereserwa Jehovha; koga Rakabhi chifeve achararama, iye nevose vari mumba naye, nokuti wakaviga nhume dzatakatuma\x + 2.4.\x*.
\v 18 Asi imwi zvirokwazvo zvichengetedzei pane zvakayereswa, zvimwe muzviite chakatukwa kana mukatora pazvakayereswa, muitise musasa waIsraeri chinhu chakatukwa\x + 2.4.\x*, muutambudze\x + Gen.. 34.30. Josh. 7.25. 1 Madz. 18.17,18. 1 Makor. 2.7.\x*.
\v 19 Asi sirivha yose negoridhe nemidziyo yendarira neyematare zvitsvene kuna Jehovha; zvichauya muchivigiro chefuma chaJehovha.
\v 20 Zvino vanhu vakadanidzira, kukaridzwa hwamanda; zvino zvakaitika vanhu pavakanzwa kurira kwehwamanda, vanhu ndokudanidzira nekudanidzira kukuru, rusvingo ndokukoromokera pasi, vanhu ndokukwira muguta, umwe neumwe pakaruramana naye, ndokutapa guta\x + 6.5. VaHeb. 11.30.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino vakaparadza chose zvose zvaiva muguta, kubva kumurume kusvika kumukadzi, kubva kumudiki kusvika kumukuru, nekusvika kunzombe, nemakwai, nembongoro, nekwakapinza kwemunondo\x + Det. 7.2.\x*.
\v 22 Zvino kuvarume vaviri vaiva vanoshora nyika, Joshua wakati: Pindai mumba memukadzi chifeve, mubudisemo mukadzi nezvose zvaanazvo, sezvamakapika kwaari\x + 2.14. VaHeb. 11.31.\x*.
\v 23 Zvino majaya, vashori, vakapinda vakabudisa Rakabhi nababa vake namai vake nehanzvadzi dzake nezvose zvaaiva nazvo; vakabudisawo hama dzake dzose; ndokuvaisa kunze kwemusasa waIsraeri\x + 2.13.\x*.
\v 24 Zvino vakapisa guta nemoto, nezvose zvaiva mariri; koga sirivha negoridhe nemidziyo yendarira neyematare vakazviisa muchivigiro chefuma cheimba yaJehovha\x + 6.19.\x*.
\v 25 Naizvozvo Rakabhi chifeve neveimba yababa vake nevose vaaiva navo, Joshua wakarega vari vapenyu; iye akagara pakati paIsraeri kusvika nhasi; nokuti wakaviga nhume Joshua dzaakatuma kunoshora Jeriko\x + Mat. 1.5.\x*.
\p
\v 26 Zvino Joshua waka\add va\add*pikisa panguva iyo achiti\x + Num.. 5.21.\x*: Wakatukwa munhu pamberi paJehovha achasimuka akavaka iri guta reJeriko; achaisa nheyo dzaro padangwe rake, agomisa mikova yaro pagotwe rake\x + 1 Madz. 16.34.\x*.
\v 27 Naizvozvo Jehovha wakava naJoshua\x + 1.5.\x*; uye mukurumbira wake waiva panyika yose\x + 9.9.\x*.